{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Kehntnsch\nus wiffu: Es tew Lahgu lah-\ngahm peckohdinaju/ ka tew man\nzittu ne ko buhs fazzijt / ka\nween/ kas keefairr eekſch ta KUN-\nGA Wahrda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Es re-\ndseju wiffu Israëln / ka tee us\nKalncem bija iſkaifiti / ittin ka\nAwis/ kam Ganna netwait. Un\ntas KUNGS fazzija : Schein\nKnngu netwait / laid eet ikkatrs\nar Meern fawa Namina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Israëta\nKehninsch us Josawatn: Woj\nes teiw ne efiru fazztjs: Ka wiꞥſch\npabr man ne labbu/ bet faunu\nween fluddina?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wehl fazzija (Mikkus:)\nTadeht klanſi ta KUNGA\nWahrdu: Es redseju to KUN-\nGu us fawu Gohda-Krehſlu feh-\nscham/ un wiffu Debbes-Speh-\nku ap winnu stahwin pa labbo\nun pa kreifo Rohku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija:\nKuesch pahrrunnahs Akabu / ka\ntas zettahs/ un friht Rahmotā\neekſch Gileadas? un weens run-\nnaja fcha/ ohtrs ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad isgahjeweens Gars/\n7. un peestahjebs ta KUNGA\nPreekſcha/ un fazzija: Es pahr-\nrunnaschu wigru. Tad fazzija\ntas KUNGS us to: Zaur fo?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazztja: Es is-\neefhu/ un buhſebu weens Mellu-\nrs wiffu Praweeschu Muttē\nWiꞥſch fazzija? Tu winnu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu raugi/ tas KUNGS\nirr weenu Mellu-Garru dewi-\nscho wiffa taiwu Praweeschu\nMuttē / un tas KUNGS ir\npahr tew taunu runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad peegahje Jedekijus/\nKnaëna Dehis/ un detve Mikkm\nweenu Plikki/ un fazzija : Kurp\nirr ta KUNGA Gars no man\nnim gahjis/ ar tew runnaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mikkus fazzija : Ran-\ngi/ tu redſefi to tai Deena / ka-\ntu no weena Kambara eekſch ob-\ntra eekſt paslehpdamers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Israëta Kehninsd\nfazzija: Neimm Mikkn/un wed-\nwinnu atpakkat pee Amonu t\nPilsfahta Wirfneeku / un pe\nJoafu ta Kehnina Dehtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fakki: Ta fakka ta-\nKehninsch: Leezeet to Zeetunn\nNamina/un ehdinajat to ar Bel-\ndu Maisi un ar Behdu Uhden-\nkamehr es ar Meernu atkat a-\ncemu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mikkus fazzija: J\nfu ar Meeru atkat atnahkti/ ta-\ntas KUNGS ne irr zaur man-\nrunnajs. Wehl fazzija wiꞥſch-\nKlaufajt wiffi Landis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta zehlahs tas Israë-\nKehninsch/un Josawats tas Ke-\nninsch no Juhda/ us Rahmot\neekſch Gileadas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Israëta Kehnins-\nfazzija us Josawatu: Es pah-\ngehrbschohs/ un nahſchu Kar-\nbet tu apgehrbees ar faiwah-\nDre\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
